00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:57.920
Li Ergou

00:00:58.520 --> 00:00:59.760
from Li Family Village in Hong Kong, China.

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.560
How many times were you arrested for feudal superstition?

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:03.480
Do you still want to be arrested?

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:05.560
Y-you... what are you saying?

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:06.560
