Oh, right, sir

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:06.360
You look pretty robust to me

00:02:07.320 --> 00:02:09.040
You are destined to live to a hundred

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:12.320
It's just that you're overworked

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.160
Try not to overthink from now on

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:16.920
