00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:55.040
Leave this clock here for now

00:07:55.560 --> 00:07:57.360
When you go under, I'll deliver it to you

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:01.280
Okay

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.760
