00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:38.360
What on earth are you thinking?

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:39.760
Why are you so nervous?

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:42.880
Have my words ever failed to come true?

00:08:44.160 --> 00:08:45.960
